sections.heading: to 76-13-9 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 2001, ch. 76, § 1 repealed 76-13-1 to 76-13-9 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1927, ch. 101, §§ 1 to 9, relating to processors of agricultural products, effective July 1, 2001. For provisions of former sections,seethe 2000 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
